name: Stay the fck home or sh*t will happen
description:
2021, gif, collage of an original watercolour painting and digital elements

Feeling depressed really sucks. But you don't wanna end up harassed by weirdos on the streets. Also, who wants to stay home forever? The solution is to become invisible... Rebel Girl has the Magic Spell. Collect her and repeat this three times: "Things seen and things not seen, let me walk here between." 

Good luck,

Jessy
